n novak contemporary art retrieved    thompson elizabeth  november  niki de saint phalle wall street international retrieved    　ニキとヨーコ  niki museum gallery nikimuseumjp in japanese and english retrieved    gelder lawrence van  october  an artist with charm and the impulse to shock the new york times retrieved    a b where the wild things art designistdreamcom  november  retrieved  november    niki de saint phalle  praemium imperiale praemium imperiale retrieved  november   the grotto by niki de saint phalle  royal gardens of herrenhausen  tourist highlights  places of interest  city tours  tourism  culture  welcome to hannover  home  hannoverde wwwhannoverde retrieved    queen califias magical circle factsheet pdf escondidoorg public art commission escondido california retrieved    public works niki charitable art foundation niki charitable art foundation ncaf retrieved     archived september   at the wayback machine  le grand oiseau amoureux museum tinguely retrieved    le bestiaire de niki de saint phalle rmn  grand palais in french réunion des musées nationaux et du grand palais des champselysées retrieved    sarah gay  firebird finds its nest at the bechtler museum of modern art charlotte viewpoint retrieved  august    la tempérance  — luxembourg nikidesaintphalleorg retrieved  may     archived february   at the wayback machine  herald scotland  november    niki de saint phalle big ganesh museum of contemporary art san diego  december  retrieved    niki de saint phalle chronology  pdf ciescondidocaus retrieved  november    public art department port of san diego retrieved    von  bis  ist die historische grotte nach den plänen der künstlerin niki de saint phalle neu ausgestaltet worden hannoverde retrieved  august    queen califias magical circle garden queencalifiaorg retrieved    a b museums  collections niki charitable art foundation niki charitable art foundation ncaf retrieved    a b c recent publications  the season of awards niki charitable art foundatio