he saint phalles wedding announcement in town and country  jeanne jacqueline harper known as jacqueline was a daughter of donald harper an american living in paris france and his wife the former jeanne bernard  according to john ashbery alexandre de saintphalle was the brother of niki de saint phalles father and also married to her mothers sister the former helen georgia harper as explained in jacqueline harper marries count american lawyers daughter marries andre de st phalle at château de fillerval the new york times  june  see john ashbery reported sightings art chronicles  carcanet  referencesedit  a b c d e f neal jane  feb  niki de saint phalle the power of playfulness telegraphcouk retrieved    january   niki charitable art foundation niki charitable art foundation retrieved    video clips niki charitable art foundation niki charitable art foundation ncaf retrieved    a b c niki de sainte phalle  september    february  pdf grand palais galeries nationales champsélysées grand palais galeries nationales champsélysées retrieved    a b c d e f g h i muchnic suzanne  may  niki de saint phalle  artist known for large colorful sculptures los angeles times retrieved    a b c d e f g h robb andy  august  niki de saint phalle  a personal journey in the public eye xamou art retrieved    a b c d e f g h i j cohen roger  october  at home with niki de saint phalle an artist her monsters her two worlds the new york times retrieved    a b c d e jansen charlotte  july  the art of niki de saint phalle a rebel through and through huffington post retrieved    a b life  work   niki charitable art foundation niki charitable art foundation retrieved    a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z aa ab ac ad ae af ag ah ai aj ak al am an ao ap aq ar as at au av aw ax ay az ba bb bc bd be bf bg bh fok kevin biografia of niki de saint phalle wwwmamgovmo civil and municipal affairs bureau of macao sar retrieved    jacqueline harper american lawyers daughter marries count andre 